 Makinde receiving the report of the state negotiation committee on Ladoke Akintola University of Technology, (LAUTECH), Ogbomosho, in Ibadan. Photo: TWITTER/SEYIAMAKINDE  It also commended the decision of the governor for the payment of arrears of pension to judicial officers in Oyo State, dating back to 2010, a feat only achievable by a proactive and accountable administration.
 
